stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Issued: passkey assertion (access + refresh)
    [*] --> AccessOnly: OTP verify (30-min access, no refresh)
    AccessOnly --> [*]: 30 min elapsed

    Issued --> Rotated: /v1/oauth/token grant_type=refresh_token
    Rotated --> Issued: new access (30 min) + new refresh (30d sliding)

    Issued --> Revoked: /v1/oauth/revoke or replay detected
    Issued --> Expired: 30 days idle
    Revoked --> [*]
    Expired --> [*]

    note right of Rotated
        Old JTI added to Redis denylist with TTL = remaining lifetime.
        Subsequent use of old refresh => replay, invalidate chain.
    end note
